as Kaimakoglou]], Greek basketball player\n*  1983   &ndash; [[Golda Marcus]], Salvadoran swimmer<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080902033403/http://results.beijing2008.cn/WRM/ENG/BIO/Athlete/4/8000894.shtml|title=MARCUS Golda|access-date=Dec 28, 2018}}</ref>\n*  1983   &ndash; [[Daryl Murphy]], Irish footballer\n*  1983   &ndash; [[Heiko Niidas]], Estonian basketball player\n*  1983   &ndash; [[Ricky Sekhon]], English actor\n*  1983   &ndash; [[Yo Yo Honey Singh]], Indian music producer\n*[[1984]] &ndash; [[Badradine Belloumou]], French-Algerian footballer\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Malin Buska]], Swedish actress\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Olivier Jean]], Canadian speed skater\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Kostas Vasileiadis]], Greek basketball player\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Wilson Aparecido Xavier J\u00fanior]], Brazilian footballer\n*[[1987]] &ndash; [[Eric Decker]], American football player\n*[[1988]] &ndash; [[\u00c9ver Guzm\u00e1n]], Mexican footballer\n*  1988   &ndash; [[James Reimer (ice hockey)|James Reimer]], Canadian ice hockey player\n*  1988   &ndash; [[Jolo Revilla]], Filipino actor and politician\n*  1988   &ndash; [[Alexander Sims (racing driver)|Alexander Sims]], English race car driver\n*[[1989]] &ndash; [[Sam Baldock]], English footballer\n*  1989   &ndash; [[Bryce Gibbs (Australian rules footballer)|Bryce Gibbs]], Australian footballer\n*  1989   &ndash; [[Sandro (footballer, born 1989)|Sandro]], Brazilian international footballer, midfielder<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=57063|title=Sandro|access-date=10 March 2020}}</ref>\n*  1989   &ndash; [[Gil Roberts]], American sprinter<ref>{{cite web |title=Gil Roberts|url=https://www.worldathletics.org/athletes/united-states/gil-roberts-221172|publisher=World Athletics|accessdate=8 February 2020}}</ref>\n*  1989   &ndash; [[Adrien Silva]], Portuguese footballer\n*  1989   &ndash; [[Caitlin Wachs]], American actress\n*[[1990]] &ndash; [[Siobhan Magnus]], American sin